Summary: Not bad, but one dog doesn't like it.
text: This isn't a bad product, but I have two small dogs, and one dog will eat most of it, but will leave some of it behind. The other dog won't even go near it. Now both my dogs are not only spoiled, but they are also used to only eating Ceasar dog food. So I can't say I would go out and buy more, but at least one of my dog's will eat it.
